<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Us!</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center;"
  >
    <div
      style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;"
    >
      <div style="background: #0b1741; padding: 0px; text-align: center; width: 100%;">
        <img
          src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/eventify-b1645.appspot.com/o/assets%2Fbanner.jpg?alt=media&token=d9455d13-5fa4-4d05-90cb-1f6cad0c3068"
          alt="Abhishek Kumar's Website Banner"
          style="max-width: 100%;"
        />
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: left;">
        <h2
          style="font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0;"
        >Hello {{name}} 👋</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 10px 0;">
          Thank you for reaching out to us. We’ve received your message and will get back to you as
          soon as possible!
        </p>
        <div style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Your Message Summary:</strong></p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Message:</strong></p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #555;">{{message}}</p>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 10px 0;">
          If you have any further queries or want to connect, feel free to reach out through our
          social media handles below.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 10px 0;">Cheers,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; margin: 10px 0;"><b>Abhishek Kumar</b></p>
      </div>
      <div
        style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #0b1741; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;"
      >
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/iamabhi0619/" style="margin: 0 10px;">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/174/174857.png"
            alt="LinkedIn"
            style="width: 25px; vertical-align: middle;"
          />
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/iamabhi0619" style="margin: 0 10px;">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733553.png"
            alt="GitHub"
            style="width: 25px; vertical-align: middle;"
          />
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/916206418701" style="margin: 0 10px;">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733585.png"
            alt="WhatsApp"
            style="width: 25px; vertical-align: middle;"
          />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/_kumar._.abhishek" style="margin: 0 10px;">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733558.png"
            alt="Instagram"
            style="width: 25px; vertical-align: middle;"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>